OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1778782268
OL,3,CPlymouth acid attack left victim's
OL,4,Cfamily 'devastated' and lives 'torn
OL,5,Capart'
OL,7,FThe family of a man who was killed in
OL,8,Fan acid attack say his death left them
OL,9,F"devastated" and their lives "torn
OL,10,Fapart".
OL,12,FDanny Cahalane was targeted outside
OL,13,Fhis home in Plymouth in February 2025
OL,14,Fand died in hospital ten weeks later.
OL,16,FThe mother of his child, Paris Wilson,
OL,17,F35, was found guilty of manslaughter
OL,18,Fand attempted kidnap, but was cleared
OL,19,Fof his murder.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
