FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1778782268
OL,3,CPlymouth acid attack left victim's
OL,4,Cfamily 'devastated' and lives 'torn
OL,5,Capart'
OL,7,FTwo men from London were found guilty
OL,8,Fof murder, and two of attempted
OL,9,Fkidnapping.
OL,11,F'Loss that will never heal'
OL,13,FIn a statement released through
OL,14,Fpolice, Mr Cahalane's family said:
OL,15,F"Today's verdict brings a sense of
OL,16,Fjustice, but it does not bring Danny
OL,17,Fback.
OL,19,F"This crime has devastated our family.
OL,20,FIt has torn lives apart and left a
OL,21,Flasting impact that cannot be undone.
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1778782268
OL,3,CPlymouth acid attack left victim's
OL,4,Cfamily 'devastated' and lives 'torn
OL,5,Capart'
OL,7,F"Danny was not just a victim. He was a
OL,8,Fson, a father and a loved one. His
OL,9,Fchildren will grow up without him and
OL,10,Fthat is a loss that will never truly
OL,11,Fheal.
OL,13,F"Danny's mum, who sadly passed away
OL,14,Fthe day after him, would have been
OL,15,Fincredibly proud to see this outcome.
OL,16,FWe take some comfort in believing she
OL,17,Fwould be standing beside us today,
OL,18,Fsupporting the fight for justice."
OL,20,F'Grief will remain forever'
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
