FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1778782268
OL,3,CPlymouth acid attack left victim's
OL,4,Cfamily 'devastated' and lives 'torn
OL,5,Capart'
OL,7,FThe court heard Mr Cahalane was a drug
OL,8,Fdealer and owed a 'large amount' of
OL,9,Fmoney to another drug dealer, known as
OL,10,F'Frost'.
OL,12,FOn Thursday, the jury returned its
OL,13,Fverdicts.
OL,15,FOn the charge of attempted kidnap,
OL,16,FParis Wilson, Jean Mukuna and Aaron
OL,17,FMukuna were found guilty. Abdulrasheed
OL,18,FAdedoja and Ramnaree Bakas were found
OL,19,Fnot guilty.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
