OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1778782268
OL,3,CPlymouth acid attack left victim's
OL,4,Cfamily 'devastated' and lives 'torn
OL,5,Capart'
OL,7,FOn the charge of murder, Abdulrasheed
OL,8,FAdedoja and Israel Augustus were found
OL,9,Fguilty. Paris Wilson, Ramnaree Bakas,
OL,10,FIsanah Sungum and Jude Hill were found
OL,11,Fnot guilty.
OL,13,FMr Cahalane's family added: "The grief
OL,14,Fwe carry will remain with us forever.
OL,15,FHowever, these verdicts do help us
OL,16,Fbegin to move forward.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
