OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1778782268
OL,3,CPlymouth acid attack left victim's
OL,4,Cfamily 'devastated' and lives 'torn
OL,5,Capart'
OL,7,F"Our focus now is on rebuilding our
OL,8,Flives and supporting Danny's children,
OL,9,Fensuring they grow up knowing who
OL,10,Ftheir father was and how deeply he was
OL,11,Floved.
OL,13,F"After such a long and difficult
OL,14,Ftrial, we now ask for privacy so that
OL,15,Fwe can grieve, reflect and begin the
OL,16,Fprocess of healing as a family."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
